[normal]The proposed introduction of a residence test for civil legal aid claimants, so as to limit legal aid to those with a “strong connection
[normal]” with the UK
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
